## ğŸš€ Deployment

### Docker
```bash
docker run -p 8000:8000 brainsait/pyheart:latest
```

### Kubernetes
```yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: pyheart
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: pyheart
  template:
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: pyheart
        image: brainsait/pyheart:latest
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8000
```

